Detailed Description

An interface the map_components element.

Member Data Documentation

attribute CellMLComponent cellml_api::MapComponents::firstComponent

The first component. This component shall be the component definition if imports have been instantiated, and otherwise shall be the ImportComponent.

attribute CellMLAttributeString cellml_api::MapComponents::firstComponentName

The name of the first component. The returned name shall be the same name as found in the component_1 attribute(that is, the implementation shall not translate the name of imported components).

attribute CellMLComponent cellml_api::MapComponents::secondComponent

The second component. This component shall be the component definition if imports have been instantiated, and otherwise shall be the ImportComponent.

attribute CellMLAttributeString cellml_api::MapComponents::secondComponentName

The name of the second component. The returned name shall be the same name as found in the component_2 attribute(that is, the implementation shall not translate the name of imported components).
